35320/extras/359b66c7d976c296e3aa469c6d0511a1.avif?t=1695263797\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135320/extras/6c560251fe255268e2325726cc264980.avif?t=1695263797\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Each replayable in a higher difficulty, from base +0 up to +5!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135320/extras/8f061f1c8b0ba55a0cb2b26d5dd83016.avif?t=1695263797\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Major Patches are released with no set schedule whenever content is ready and (hopefully) bug-free<br></li><li> Minor Patches are released with no set schedule whenever bug fixes or changes are ready</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Only Windows with mouse and keyboard are natively supported right now, but more ways to play are planned!</li></ul>",
